{
  "stem": "1183.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We heard later on that-- even while we were on the train we heard that-- you know rumors fly always-- that in cattle cars we were deported to, and we ended up in Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Philips tried desperately to save us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they even sent a cable to Auschwitz, but we were in the middle of Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was not-- they were not-- they were unable to, to save us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the train went on, and this was the Jewish part of the Philips Group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The non-Jewish part of the Philips Group was-- and the women were deported in September 1943, and they were sent to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's also well known camp, R-A-V-E-N-S-B-R-U-C-K.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's for the non-Jewish women from Philips in September.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then the camp was no camp anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived during the night in Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A commanding officer was standing while I was on the platform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had some small children with us from Philips, but we all remained in one group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, this is the Philips Group from Eindhoven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, now we'll name it from Eindhoven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were all headed into shower rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there we had to take our clothes off and remain there the whole night without any clothing, without food naturally, nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The next morning the inmates came and told us what kind of a camp Birkenau-Auschwitz was, what was going on, and crematoria, and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we were all tattooed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all got a number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all shocked anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- you, you were more or less an automaton.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- it's, it's-- I don't know if I can recall any, any, any, any, any thought.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were scared, yes, but you behaved with group.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
